Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.53,0:00:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kabar?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.53,0:00:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, Morimo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.53,0:00:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Selamat pagi.\N- Apa kabar?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.07,0:00:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Hei, Mini! Hai!\N- Kau sedang apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.03,0:00:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iseng saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.16,0:01:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tani! Selamat pagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.21,0:01:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat pagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.42,0:01:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seram.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.50,0:01:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak ada yang tanya!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.75,0:01:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Minggir atau kuhancurkan sanggul rambutmu!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.92,0:01:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hentikan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.88,0:01:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika tidak bergegas, kalian akan terlambat!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.51,0:01:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku berangkat!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.24,0:01:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat pagi, Suzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.65,0:01:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Azuma! Selamat pagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.07,0:01:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau dan Taira datang bersama?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.07,0:02:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.37,0:02:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat pagi, Nabesato!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.91,0:02:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Selamat pagi.\N- Selamat pagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.16,0:02:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, Yamada!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.91,0:02:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.91,0:02:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh! Tani! Selamat pagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.13,0:02:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat pagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.88,0:02:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suzuki, berisik sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.97,0:02:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Salam yang benar akan menyelamatkan dunia!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.93,0:02:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, bulu mataku bagus hari ini, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.56,0:02:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak tahu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.35,0:02:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa tidak memakai bulu mata palsu saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.14,0:02:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bisa saja,\Ntapi aku lebih suka bulu mata asliku.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.94,0:02:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maskara akan luntur jika kau berkeringat,\Nmenangis, atau menggosoknya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.03,0:02:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, akhirnya aku bertanya-tanya\Nmerek apa yang harus kucoba…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.66,0:02:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan semacamnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.66,0:02:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tani, bagaimana menurutmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.17,0:02:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak tahu apa pun soal itu, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.96,0:02:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tani! Kau dingin\Nseperti biasanya hari ini!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.05,0:02:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kau senang sekali mengganggu Tani
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.47,0:03:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tentang hal yang bukan minatnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.30,0:03:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.22,0:03:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku suka caranya membungkamku.\NAku tidak bisa menahan diri.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.27,0:03:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika kau butuh bantuan memilih maskara,\Naku akan membantu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.35,0:03:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak perlu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.31,0:03:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dibungkam lagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.52,0:03:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia kejam.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.98,0:03:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berhentilah mengganggu Tani.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.82,0:03:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tani, maafkan aku. Sungguh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.49,0:03:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sejujurnya…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.33,0:03:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku sangat mencintaimu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.92,0:05:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}PR bahasa Inggris-mu sudah selesai?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.63,0:05:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku hanya mengerjakan bagian\Nyang kupikir akan benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.05,0:05:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kerjakan semuanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.01,0:05:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang duduk di kursi sebelahku adalah Tani.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.56,0:05:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia tampak seperti pria pendiam\Nberkacamata bagi orang lain,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.06,0:05:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi Tani mengutarakan pikirannya\Ndengan jelas.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.07,0:05:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Guru mungkin akan menandai bagian ini,\Njadi, harus dikerjakan ulang.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.11,0:05:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa? Kenapa? Sudah cukup bagus, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.87,0:05:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dan sikapnya sama\Ndengan siapa pun dia bersama.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.08,0:05:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau sudah dapat tugasmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.50,0:05:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tugas?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.75,0:05:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih sudah mengumpulkannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.13,0:05:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.21,0:05:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seperti kali terakhir\Nkami bertukar tempat duduk…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.30,0:05:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah. Tukar tempat duduk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.69,0:05:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tepat di sampingnya!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.02,0:05:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini gila. Aku harus bagaimana?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.98,0:06:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kuharap kau baik denganku, Tetangga!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.28,0:06:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sama-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.74,0:06:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Masalah di barisan depan…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.91,0:06:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Papan tulis bisa lebih sulit dibaca.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.37,0:06:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan membacakan apa pun\Nyang tidak bisa kau lihat, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.49,0:06:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kurasa aku akan baik-baik saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.21,0:06:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.29,0:06:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tani tidak menyesuaikan perilakunya\Ntanpa alasan bagus.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.46,0:06:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sangat mengagumi itu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.09,0:06:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suzuki, mana yang kau suka?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.51,0:06:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa? Maaf, aku tidak mendengarkan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.35,0:06:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.26,0:06:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi maksudku…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.31,0:06:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kurasa orang
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.60,0:06:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}akan memeriahkan suasana lebih baik\Ndaripada rekaman audio.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.81,0:06:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan begitu, Tani?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.94,0:06:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak tahu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.52,0:06:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tani, jika dia mengganggumu, katakan saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.24,0:06:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.78,0:06:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lihat? Dia bilang tidak apa-apa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.83,0:06:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Fiuh! Syukurlah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.04,0:07:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tani, maafkan aku!\NAku mencintaimu, tapi…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.08,0:07:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin bicara normal denganmu, tapi…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.92,0:07:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku selalu mengkhawatirkan\Npandangan orang lain terhadapku,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.30,0:07:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}jadi, aku tidak bisa bicara dengan cara\Nyang menunjukkan aku menyukaimu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.42,0:07:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sangat mengagumi Tani, tapi…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.39,0:07:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kau dan aku bertolak belakang!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.85,0:07:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar! Sepulang sekolah, ayo ke KingBurg!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.39,0:07:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, Suzuki! Kau juga ikut, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.94,0:07:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku harus mengerjakan PR.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.57,0:07:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku pasti ikut!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.41,0:07:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hore!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.41,0:07:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suzuki, bolehkah aku menyalin PR-mu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.37,0:07:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.79,0:07:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tolong aku!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.75,0:07:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah. Kau payah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.92,0:07:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.67,0:07:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suzuki!\NCeritamu kemarin membuatku tertawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.96,0:07:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suzuki, boleh aku mengikuti akunmu juga?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.05,0:07:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak mengunggah hal aneh, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.18,0:07:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu! Silakan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.56,0:07:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi kau tahu…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.64,0:07:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tani sangat pintar, bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.69,0:08:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maksudmu tugas kelompok hari ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.60,0:08:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setelah kau mengatakannya,\Naku melihatnya pergi ke tempat les.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.90,0:08:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa? Apa dia menuju UTokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.61,0:08:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak tahu soal itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.03,0:08:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia sungguh luar biasa, bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.28,0:08:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia hidup di dunia yang berbeda\Ndari kita semua.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.28,0:08:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan samakan aku denganmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.70,0:08:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suzuki yang paling dekat dengan Tani\Ndi grup kita, bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.33,0:08:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa? Menurutmu begitu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.79,0:08:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menjijikkan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.04,0:08:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.13,0:08:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku cuma mudah tersedak di usia ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.01,0:08:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau terlalu muda.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.66,0:08:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}SudaKen memenangkan\NAktor Paling Dicintai untuk kali kedua!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.22,0:08:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Para gadis sangat menyukai\Ntipe yang nakal, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.47,0:08:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hanya SudaKen yang cocok menjadi pacar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.23,0:08:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu dia! Suzuki mengagumi SudaKen lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.73,0:08:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada yang bilang membaca situasi itu\Ndemi kebaikan orang lain…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.65,0:08:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi bukan begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.40,0:08:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku melakukannya demi diriku sendiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.58,0:09:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.17,0:09:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}terkadang itu membuatku lelah. Kenapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.89,0:09:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku harus pulang.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.32,0:09:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tani, kau mau pulang sekarang?\NIni sudah sore, bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.41,0:09:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tahu wajahku pasti\Nterlihat jelek sekarang!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.95,0:09:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada tugas komite yang harus diserahkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.54,0:09:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tani, kau pulang lewat mana?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.37,0:09:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Keluar gerbang dan belok kanan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.29,0:09:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.58,0:09:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak ada yang lihat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.96,0:09:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tani…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.38,0:09:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gawat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.22,0:10:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mau pulang bersama?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.76,0:10:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jantungku mau meledak!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.27,0:10:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, Tani, rumahmu juga lewat sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.77,0:10:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi kita belum pernah pulang bersama.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.94,0:10:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.03,0:10:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku selalu berlarian sepulang sekolah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.24,0:10:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pantas saja aku tidak pernah melihatmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.79,0:10:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau juga ada urusan OSIS, bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.87,0:10:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.68,0:10:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu kami pergi ke KingBurg tempo hari,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.01,0:10:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan burgernya besar sekali!\NBahkan tidak muat di dalam roti.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.77,0:10:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rotinya malah disajikan di samping.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.39,0:10:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak tahu cara memakannya!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.23,0:10:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu. Apa topik ini menarik?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.48,0:10:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa itu enak?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.19,0:10:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya! Benar! Enak sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.66,0:11:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tahu! Tani, mau makan denganku?\NHanya bercanda!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.20,0:11:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.37,0:11:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.33,0:11:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang dia katakan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.46,0:11:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa dia hanya bersikap sopan?\NAtau menyesuaikan suasana?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.55,0:11:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, Tani bukan orang seperti itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.06,0:11:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Temukan sesuatu…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.60,0:11:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Katakan sesuatu kepadanya, Diriku!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.56,0:11:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gawat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.86,0:11:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jantungku berdebar kencang!\NAku tidak bisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.11,0:11:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.48,0:12:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak mungkin.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.28,0:12:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.07,0:12:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mimpi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.74,0:12:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa? Aku harus bagaimana?\NSaat ini, aku…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.16,0:12:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku yakin tanganku berkeringat banyak.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.21,0:12:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Detak jantungku sangat keras hingga bisa\Nkudengar berdebar di telingaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.34,0:12:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa aku mau mati?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.85,0:12:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}AKU KE ARAH SINI…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.77,0:12:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak ingat bagaimana
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.69,0:12:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku pulang setelah itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.73,0:12:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sampai di rumah setelah itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.98,0:12:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}YA. SAMPAI NANTI…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.44,0:13:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku pu…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.36,0:13:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan berbaring di pintu masuk!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.74,0:13:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh. Kak.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.16,0:13:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seram!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.08,0:13:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami berpegangan tangan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.13,0:13:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tidak mau makan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.46,0:13:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika kau tidak mau makan, berikan kepadaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.09,0:13:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dan…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.09,0:13:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dia memegang tanganku!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.80,0:13:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini gila!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.26,0:13:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana aku menghadapi\Nsemua orang di sekolah besok?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.85,0:13:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jantungku berdebar kencang!\NAku tidak akan pernah bisa tidur!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.48,0:13:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Diam!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.62,0:13:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aduh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.87,0:13:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aduh…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.04,0:13:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pagi? Yang benar saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.42,0:14:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu. Pukul berapa ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.09,0:14:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku belum pernah absen atau terlambat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.89,0:14:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.80,0:14:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di mana semua orang?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.93,0:14:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.73,0:14:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini lebih seperti tengah hari\Ndaripada pagi hari.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.90,0:14:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku merasa percuma bergegas.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.15,0:14:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mari kita panaskan ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.45,0:14:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah jam makan siang, tapi selamat pagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.62,0:14:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suzuki, kau jarang terlambat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.41,0:14:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau bisa saja mengambil cuti saat ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.75,0:14:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku ingin ikut\Nkelas olahraga pilihan kita.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.04,0:14:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dasar bodoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.21,0:14:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suzuki! Kau di sini!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.00,0:14:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya! Hai!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.80,0:14:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, apa kau dan Tani berpacaran?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.64,0:14:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.51,0:14:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gapacho bilang\Nkalian pulang bersama kemarin.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.60,0:14:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa Gapacho?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.19,0:14:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan orang lain?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.65,0:15:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gapacho tahu apa yang dilihatnya!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.31,0:15:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan urusan kita.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.94,0:15:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, tunggu, Yamada.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.73,0:15:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat ini,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.74,0:15:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kami berada di fase "mungkin saling suka,\Ntapi belum dipastikan".
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.95,0:15:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Fase yang paling rumit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.08,0:15:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini bukan sesuatu yang bisa kau usik\Nuntuk bersenang-senang!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.62,0:15:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bertindak serius!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.83,0:15:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu maksudku…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.17,0:15:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- seseorang melihat kami\N- Lalu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.79,0:15:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Melihat kita di mana?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.67,0:15:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.68,0:15:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan begitu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.23,0:15:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tahu…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.90,0:15:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu kursiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.40,0:15:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Boleh kuambil buku catatanku?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.61,0:15:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa? Maaf. Aku akan pindah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.74,0:15:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak apa-apa. Kita pindah\Ndi jam pelajaran berikutnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.78,0:15:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.13,0:16:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak mungkin lebih buruk.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.71,0:16:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tubuh mengurai karbohidrat,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.26,0:16:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan kadar gula darah meningkat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.34,0:16:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia mendengarku menyangkalnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.76,0:16:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu sangat tidak sopan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.02,0:16:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau salah paham! Aku tidak bermaksud\Nmengatakannya seperti itu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.02,0:16:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tani, maafkan aku…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.48,0:16:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak! Tidak akan pernah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.24,0:16:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku ingin segera minta maaf!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.24,0:16:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku harus bagaimana?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.45,0:16:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kuharap Tani tidak merasa buruk sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.20,0:16:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku benci ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.12,0:16:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suzuki, kau belum memungut satu kok pun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.04,0:16:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suzuki, kau belum memungut satu kok pun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.87,0:16:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pungut saja dengan tanganmu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.46,0:16:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa aku selalu…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.55,0:16:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, Suzuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.26,0:16:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bicara.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.31,0:17:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku harus bicara dengannya!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.89,0:17:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cepat jelaskan kesalahpahaman ini!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.39,0:17:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi di sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.23,0:17:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di sini, tempat semua orang berada?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.16,0:17:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suzuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.03,0:17:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tani…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.91,0:17:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tolong lupakan kejadian kemarin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.63,0:17:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maafkan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.43,0:17:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo, Suzuki! Kupon berondong ini\Nkedaluwarsa hari ini!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.48,0:17:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, bukankah kau baru bicara dengan Tani?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.15,0:17:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian benar-benar akur, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.82,0:17:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suzuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.61,0:17:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau juga?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.74,0:17:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lakukan lagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.83,0:18:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.71,0:18:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}jatuh cinta kepada Tani.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.46,0:18:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.96,0:18:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cintaku bertepuk sebelah tangan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.34,0:18:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.88,0:18:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dan kemarin…\Naku mengajaknya pulang bersamaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.47,0:18:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa itu salah?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.35,0:18:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.85,0:18:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.27,0:18:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa? Seharusnya kau memberitahuku!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.31,0:18:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa pun akan mengira kalian cuma bertemu\Ndalam perjalanan pulang!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.11,0:18:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa yang akan mengira\Nitu situasi yang serius?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.32,0:18:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa? Tunggu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.65,0:18:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ucap hal tak peka saat makan siang.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.62,0:18:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau selalu tidak peka.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.20,0:18:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, Tani sudah pergi. Tidak apa-apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.21,0:18:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.29,0:18:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau mungkin bisa menyusul jika berlari!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.04,0:18:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini penting, Suzuki! Kejar!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.96,0:18:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan cemaskan berondongnya!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.72,0:18:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf! Aku tak peduli!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.88,0:18:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.43,0:19:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lari, Suzuki! Tunjukkan kecepatan\Nyang tidak akan mempermalukan namamu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.06,0:19:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau Suzuki, bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.48,0:19:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selambat apa kau ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.40,0:19:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tancap gas!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.98,0:19:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lihat ke depan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.03,0:19:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.66,0:19:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.37,0:19:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mengatakan perasaanku dengan lantang…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.04,0:19:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa semudah ini melakukannya?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.93,0:19:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku menyerah pada godaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.39,0:19:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hanya itu yang bisa kukatakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.06,0:19:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suzuki duduk di sampingku.\NDia selalu bicara denganku,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.44,0:19:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi dia tidak peduli padaku\Nsecara pribadi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.48,0:19:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cuma kelakar ringan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.40,0:20:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mau pulang bersama?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.70,0:20:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itulah yang kupikirkan, tapi…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.71,0:20:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hari ini…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.88,0:20:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kukira dia tak akan datang ke sekolah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.47,0:20:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan begitu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.47,0:20:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak lama kemudian, aku terbiasa\Ndengan Suzuki yang bicara denganku.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.98,0:20:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sehari tanpanya…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.90,0:20:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tani!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.48,0:20:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terasa terlalu sepi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.57,0:20:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mencintaimu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.25,0:20:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tani, maaf aku mengganggumu\Ndengan hal-hal bodoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.71,0:21:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf atas ucapanku\Ndi depan semua orang hari ini!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.76,0:21:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak tahu cara bicara denganmu, Tani.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.68,0:21:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku takut semua orang\Nakan melihat perasaanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.39,0:21:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku manusia yang sangat menyedihkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.40,0:21:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.77,0:21:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tani, aku ingin lebih sering bersamamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.40,0:21:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat kau memegang tanganku,\Nitu membuatku sangat bahagia.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.78,0:21:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sangat bahagia hingga aku\Ntidak bisa tidur semalam dan ketiduran.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.79,0:21:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maksudku, itu seperti,\N"Kau akhirnya tidur," bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.79,0:21:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.00,0:21:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.22,0:21:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat kau tidak bicara,\Naku tidak tahu harus bagaimana.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.64,0:21:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku manusia menyedihkan seperti itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.60,0:21:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kau… tak keberatan dengan itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.07,0:22:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ekspresi wajahmu sangat menggemaskan!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.99,0:22:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.95,0:22:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maksudku, itu hanya…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.86,0:22:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah itu sudah jelas?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.33,0:22:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku merasa membuatmu menangis.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.83,0:22:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu karena memang begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.54,0:22:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maskara, bukan? Itu akan hilang, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.09,0:22:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau benar-benar menyimak, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.85,0:22:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gawat!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.14,0:22:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Apa? Kenapa? Apa penyebabnya?\N- Jantungku berdebar-debar!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.31,0:22:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang benar saja.
